Type of Feat: General
You have trained extensively in heavy armor, and you have learned to take advantage of the protection it offers.
Prerequisite: Armor Proficiency (Heavy), Base Attack Bonus +4
Benefit: When you are wearing heavy armor, lessen the armor check penalty by 1 and increase the armor bonus by 1. This is done as a +skill bonus to (Hide, Move Silently, and Tumble) and a +1 Dodge AC bonus.
Special: A fighter can choose Heavy Armor Optimization as one of his bonus fighter feats.
Use: Automatic.